 Allah raises his wisdom if he humbles himself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubaydullah ibn \u2018Adi reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said upon the pulpit, \u201cVerily, if a servant humbles himself for Allah Almighty, he will increase his wisdom.\u201d Source: Juz\u2019 fi\u0304hi\u0304 H\u0323adi\u0304th Sufya\u0304n ibn \u2018Uyaynah 24 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20817,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/08\/11\/umar-khalifah-favors-jew\/","url_meta":{"origin":40275,"position":5},"title":"Umar on Judgment: The Caliph judges in favor of the Jew","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn al-Musayyib reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, was presented with a dispute between a Muslim and a Jew. Umar believed that the truth was on the side of the Jew, so he passed judgment in his favor. The Jew said to him, \u201cBy Allah,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/40275","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abu